meta_description:
Speaking to the American people in the wake of a devastating terror attack at the Kabul airport that left scores dead on Thursday –– including numerous U.S. troops –– President Joe Biden promised the U.S. would strike back against those responsible.
"To those who carried out this attack, as well as anyone who wishes America harm, know this –– we will not forgive, we will not forget, we will hunt you down and make you pay,” the president said in a somber White House address.
